file.name: simple-api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: simple-api
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /api/messages:
    get:
      summary: Your GET endpoint
      tags: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Message'
      operationId: get-api-messages
components:
  schemas:
    Message:
      title: Message
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        text:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
        - text
